ertes-20200306105931.html |title=La Comunidad de Madrid registra 137 positivos por coronavirus y dos muertes |date=6 March 2020 |access-date=6 March 2020 |newspaper=[[Infosalus]] |publisher=Europa Press Noticias S.A. |language=es}}</ref> including a 76-year-old man with previous pathologies who died at the Infanta Elena Hospital of [[Valdemoro]], the fourth confirmed death in Spain,<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.20minutos.es/noticia/4177544/0/muere-mujer-coronavirus-valdemoro/ |title=Muere otro hombre de 76 a\u00f1os en Madrid con coronavirus en una residencia de Valdemoro con otros 16 contagiados |date=6 March 2020 |access-date=6 March 2020 |newspaper=[[20 Minutos]] |publisher=20 Minutos Editora S.L. |language=es}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.telemadrid.es/noticias/madrid/Segunda-Madrid-producido-Valdemoro-positivo-0-2210778901--20200306084058.html |title=Un centro de mayores de Valdemoro registra la segunda muerte en Madrid con coronavirus |date=6 March 2020 |access-date=6 March 2020 |newspaper=[[Telemadrid]] |publisher=Madrid autonomous government |language=es}}</ref> other 91 years old man dead at the [[Gregorio Mara\u00f1\u00f3n Hospital]]<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.europapress.es/madrid/noticia-hombre-91-anos-patologia-previa-tercera-victima-mortal-madrid-coronavirus-20200306183223.html |title=Un hombre de 91 a\u00f1os con patolog\u00eda previa, tercera v\u00edctima mortal en Madrid por coronavirus |date=6 March 2020 |access-date=6 March 2020 |newspaper=[[Europa Press]] |publisher=Europa Press Noticias S.A. |language=es}}</ref> and another 83 years old man deceased at the Severo Ochoa Hospital in [[Legan\u00e9s]].<ref name=\"auto13\">{{cite news |url=https://www.europapress.es/madrid/noticia-hombre-83-anos-patologias-previas-cuatro-muerto-madrid-coronavirus-20200306205601.html |title=Un hombre de 83 a\u00f1os con patolog\u00edas previas, cuarto muerto en Madrid por coronavirus |date=6 March 2020 |access-date=6 March 2020 |newspaper=[[Europa 